title: Anaal Nathrakh - In The Constellation Of The Black Widow
description:
Anaal Nathrakh's newest album in lossless .flac. And obviously the 9th track "Satanarchist" is intact unlike in some of the releases out there. Please do bear with it I only have a 8/1 connection.

7.  The Lucifer Effect
8.  Oil Upon The Sores Of Lepers

10. Blood Eagles Carved On The Backs Of Innocents
